71004221210000.Long Description:
Inspired by traditional Hawaiian quilt designs, the Ailani quilt offers a handguided outline and vermicelli quilting which accentuates the printed large scale cream medallion on a light sage ground. A sophisticated master bedroom design.

Twin - 68-in. x 86-in. 
Queen - 90-in. x 90-in. 
King - 104-in. x 90-in.
Standard Sham - 20-in. x 26-in. 
Decorative Pillow - 12-in. x 24-in.
